        <h2 class="section-title mb-lg">Common Scam Red Flags</h2>

        <div class="articles-list mb-xl">
          <article class="article-item" style="background: #f8d7da;">
            <div class="article-content">
              <h4 style="color: #721c24;">Price is Too Low</h4>
              <p style="color: #721c24;">A boat priced significantly below market value is often a scam. Research fair prices in our photo gallery.</p>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="article-item" style="background: #f8d7da;">
            <div class="article-content">
              <h4 style="color: #721c24;">Seller is "Out of Town"</h4>
              <p style="color: #721c24;">Scammers claim they can't meet in person. They're military, missionaries, or recently relocated.</p>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="article-item" style="background: #f8d7da;">
            <div class="article-content">
              <h4 style="color: #721c24;">Requests Wire Transfer or Gift Cards</h4>
              <p style="color: #721c24;">Legitimate sellers accept normal payment methods. Wire transfers and gift cards cannot be reversed.</p>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="article-item" style="background: #f8d7da;">
            <div class="article-content">
              <h4 style="color: #721c24;">Uses an "Escrow" Service You've Never Heard Of</h4>
              <p style="color: #721c24;">Fake escrow websites are common. Only use well-known services and verify independently.</p>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="article-item" style="background: #f8d7da;">
            <div class="article-content">
              <h4 style="color: #721c24;">Pressure to Act Fast</h4>
              <p style="color: #721c24;">Scammers create urgency. A legitimate seller will give you time to verify.</p>
            </div>
          </article>
        </div>

        <div class="sidebar-card mb-xl">
          <h2>How to Protect Yourself</h2>
          <ul style="margin-left: var(--space-lg);">
            <li style="margin-bottom: var(--space-md); list-style: disc;">
              <strong>See the boat in person</strong> before sending any money
            </li>
            <li style="margin-bottom: var(--space-md); list-style: disc;">
              <strong>Verify ownership</strong> - check the title and registration
            </li>
            <li style="margin-bottom: var(--space-md); list-style: disc;">
              <strong>Meet at the boat's location</strong> - don't have it "shipped" to you
            </li>
            <li style="margin-bottom: var(--space-md); list-style: disc;">
              <strong>Use secure payment</strong> - cash at closing, cashier's check, or known escrow
            </li>
            <li style="margin-bottom: var(--space-md); list-style: disc;">
              <strong>Research the seller</strong> - search their email and phone online
            </li>
            <li style="margin-bottom: var(--space-md); list-style: disc;">
              <strong>Trust your instincts</strong> - if something feels wrong, walk away
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

